sequenceDiagram
  participant Browser
  participant API
  participant Auth
  participant TenantRouter
  participant Service
  participant DB
  Browser->>API: HTTP request
  API->>Auth: resolve session or public route
  Auth->>TenantRouter: tenant id if authenticated
  TenantRouter->>DB: tenant/control connection
  API->>Service: validated operation
  Service->>DB: query/update
  Service-->>API: result
  API-->>Browser: JSON/redirect/page
